#Event Tracker ReadMe

# What This Project Does
This is a REST API built with Express and MongoDB.
It allows users to create, read, update, and delete journal entries.

## How to Run It
1. Run npm install
2. Make sure MongoDB is running
3. Run node server.js
4. Test routes in Postman

## Main Routes
GET /tasks
GET /tasks/:id
POST /notes
PUT /notes/:id
DELETE /notes/:id
